Housemate Venita Akpofure, has been evicted from the 2019 Big Brother Naija reality TV show. She was evicted on Sunday night after she pulled the lowest number of votes for the week. Housemates up for eviction with her; Frodd, Omashola, Khafi and Elozonam escaped going home. Venita came into the House on July 30th alongside Elozanam. Venita is a mother of two, who was a former video vixen, an actress before she got married and took time off the screen. She has since announced the end of her marriage. On her entry into the House, she had promised to bring a blend of confusion, fun, heat and drama to the Pepper Dem House.